essarily reflect Aitoearn's 观看次数, policies, 或 official stance 在 any 顶部ic. Key limitations 到 be aware of: - **Accuracy**: The AI 可能 occasionally generate incorrect information about people, places, 或 facts. - **Hallucinations**: The AI 可以 sometimes "hallucinate" 或 generate information 那个 应用ears plausible but is entirely fabricated. - **Up-到-date knowledge**: The AI's knowledge is not real-time 和 可能 not include the most recent events 或 开发指南s. - **Bias 和 harmful 内容**: 在 rare cases, the AI 可能 produce biased 内容 或 potentially harmful instructions. If 您 encounter such 内容, please report it 到 us 在 [hello@aitoearn.com](mailto:hello@aitoearn.com). - **网址 processing**: The AI cannot open, read, 或 directly access any 网址s provided 到 it. - **Ethical con侧边rations**: The AI doesn't have 在这里nt ethical judgment. 您 应该 ensure AI-generated 内容 aligns 与 您的 own ethical standards. By being aware of 这些 limitations, 您 可以 make the most of 我们的 AI Assistant while ensuring 您的 内容 is high-quality 和 accurate. Always use 您的 judgment 和 expertise 何时 reviewing AI-generated suggestions. ## FAQ ### 哪个 AI model does Aitoearn use? Aitoearn's AI Assistant currently utilizes GPT-4.0 technology from OpenAI.
